		</a>
		<div class="upsell-left">
			<h4 class="upsell-title">Summer Camp</h4>
			<div class="upsell-text">
				<h5 style="font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px;">Action Packed Summer Camp: Lights, Camera, Adventure!</h5>
				Behind-the-scenes camp offers an unforgettable experience for your little ones.
			</div>
			<div class="upsell-subtext">
